parameters:
Yay! It's big sis!!! You really came to help me after
all...! I'm so touched... for me...!!

Big sis said she won't stop, you know. You're the older one
here. Step away from the door... it's annoying.
しばらくベガの開錠のカチャカチャSE
Oh my... Oh? And who might this lovely young lady be?
ラウラ左右をキョロキョロ
T-to call me lovely... something like that...///
You're Laura. You're like a temporary ally, huh.

Miss Laura! I am Cat! I am an informant, so please remember
me as Cat the Informant!

As you can see, I may look like a wreck, but I'm actually
quite capable. That's why I came all the way here to help.

Ah...!! Big sis's carrot and stick...! This Cat... gets
excited and wet...!!

Ugh, you're so annoying. Making me waste my time... Fine,
I'll open it.

Ah...! The fresh air of the outside world...!! I am...
currently experiencing the sensation of being alive!

Yes, yes. It's considered an escape until we get outside. So
be quiet for a little while until then.

Your companions are probably a little further inside. This
nonsense can be somewhat useful, so let's get it over with
quickly.
アイテムサポートと多少の物理攻撃。
